yaz-screenshot (0.1.1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Fix empty .deb: debian/rules was staging files under debian/yaz/
    (the old binary-package name) while debian/control declares the
    binary as yaz-screenshot, so debhelper assembled the .deb from an
    empty debian/yaz-screenshot/ tree. Renamed the staging prefix.

